data.description: One story home located on an oversized lot (.46) of an acre in Keller ISD! This home welcomes you with a lovely covered front porch. Upon entry you will find the dining room featuring a large built in hutch and a cute bay window seat. The Living room has a vaulted ceiling, fireplace with white birch gas logs and patio & pool access.  Wonderful kitchen with Corian countertops, breakfast bar, SS appliances and an abundance of storage cabinets. Primary bedroom has dual closets, pool access, plus a walk-in closet off the master bath. Secondary bedrooms are generous in size. Enjoy your own backyard Oasis with a 16x7 covered patio, and an inground Gunite diving pool. Updates include pool replaster, tile, coping and decking all replaced in 2022. Roof & HVAC replaced in 2019. Dishwasher replaced 2023. Great location with two nearby parks. Just minutes away from shopping, dining, and major highways.
